'''Mithril equipment''' are items made from [[Metal#Basic metals|mithril metal]]. Mithril equipment is stronger than [[black equipment]], but weaker than [[adamant equipment]]. All mithril items are coloured with a dark shade of blue. Mithril armour requires 20 [[Defence]] to equip, and mithril weapons require 20 [[Attack]]. They are notably popular due to being lighter than equipment made of other conventional metals, while still providing a fair amount of bonuses.

==Weapons==
'''Mithril weapons''' require an [[Attack]] level of 20 to wield.

===One-handed melee weapons===
